Description: Real-time system monitoring tool with dual-axis frequency plots
 System Monitor Tool provides real-time monitoring of CPU, GPU, NPU,
 and memory usage with a graphical user interface built on PyQt5.
 .
 Features include:
  * Dual-axis real-time plots showing usage and frequency together
  * Per-core CPU usage, frequency, and temperature monitoring
  * GPU monitoring with Intel (i915/Xe), NVIDIA, and AMD support
  * Intel NPU monitoring (Meteor Lake, Arrow Lake, Lunar Lake)
  * Memory and swap usage tracking with detailed metrics
  * CPU frequency and governor control
  * Comprehensive data export (CSV, JSON, HTML with 13+ interactive charts)
  * Color-coded visual legends for easy identification
  * Historical data logging to SQLite database
  * Low-overhead design for minimal system impact
